{"type":"text","timestamp":1775875688650,"sessionID":"ses_2859188c7ffe1jYyOXtLUWppts","part":{"id":"prt_d7a707c2d001WOnMX3EFOsGkhe","messageID":"msg_d7a706086001JSVDlFbjzSWvJN","sessionID":"ses_2859188c7ffe1jYyOXtLUWppts","type":"text","text":"Done. The proposal.md for AR-024 has been written with:\n\n- **Purpose**: DockerService encapsulation for container image lifecycle management (build, push, remove)\n- **Scope**: Complete DockerService with `_docker_login_sdk`, `_tag_image_sdk`, `_get_image_info` additions\n- **Impact Analysis**: Dependencies on `docker>=6.0.0`, consumers are BuildRuntime and PublishRuntime\n- **Alternatives**: Rejected subprocess CLI, REST API, and service splitting\n- **Risks**: Docker daemon availability, registry auth failures, image tagging\n- **Implementation Checklist**: 10 items covering method additions and tests","time":{"start":1775875688649,"end":1775875688649}}}
